<div class="container">

  <div class="row justify-content-center text-center p-4 mt-4 mb-4" style="background-color:#00000088">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <%= image_tag("brand/logo.png", class: "d-block mx-auto", style: "width:70%") %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6 d-block my-auto">
      <h1 class="text-white text-special">Welcome to Pick'Em!</h1>
      <p class="text-white text-special">Predict Major Dota League Games to Win Prizes!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-center text-center p-4 mt-4 mb-4" style="background-color:#ff555588">
    <div class="col-lg-12 d-block my-auto">
      <h2 class="text-white text-special">Upcoming Entry!</h2>
      <p class="text-white text-special">The International 2019</p>
      <%= image_tag("brand/upcoming.png", class: "d-block mx-auto", style: "width:80%;") %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-center p-4 mt-4 mb-4" style="background-color:#5555ff88">
    <div class="col-lg-12 d-block my-auto">
      <h2 class="text-white text-special text-center">How To Participate</h2>
        <p>
          <span class="badge badge-info">Step 1 </span> Signed Up for Pickemd2 and completed verification process.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="badge badge-info">Step 2</span> Predict 5 questions per match for all matches in the published Tournament.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="badge badge-info">Step 3</span> Each correct prediction earn 1 point and player accumulated most point throughout the Tournament will win the prize!
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="badge badge-info">Step 4</span> Player must complete all predictions 60 minutes prior to official per match time to avoid any complications.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="badge badge-info">Step 5</span> Once the tournament is ended and when the top scorers are finalized, our Admin will contact winner for awarding the prize within 3days!
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="badge badge-info">Step 6</span> Please do not hesitate to contact via whatsapp to admin contact or email to us.
        </p>
      </div>
  </div>

</div>